{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709350/extras/PageDescription_BatBoy.png?t=1713411028\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709350/extras/azaros_fight.gif?t=1713411028\" /><br><br>Play as Bat Boy in this 2D side-scrolling action platformer in which the interdimensional mage <strong>Lord Vicious</strong> has brainwashed Bat Boy\u2019s fellow teammates in order to participate in the <strong>Trials of Darkness</strong>, a heinously brutal series of athletic events! It\u2019s up to Bat Boy to team up with the mouthy crow <i>Garou</i>, traversing a hostile world, to free the minds of his sports-hero teammates and learn their skills before they fall victim to the Trials. Along the way, Bat Boy will encounter all manner of characters, some allies, most not, as he fights his way through the bad guys in a variety of levels until reaching the final confrontation with <strong>Lord Vicious</strong>.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709350/extras/gemdrop1.gif?t=1713411028\" /><br><br>Bat Boy pits the titular hero against the former allies of his sports team, heroes such as <i>Racket Girl</i>, <i>Shinai Guy</i>, <i>Aquaria</i> and <i>Mr. Blitzer</i>, among others as he travels through the many regions beyond <strong>Lord Vicious'</strong> dimensional gateway!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709350/extras/swoop.gif?t=1713411028\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709350/extras/PageDescription_Features.png?t=1713411028\" /><br><strong>\u25aa</strong> A thrilling <strong>2D platforming adventure</strong> set against rich, nostalgic 8-bit backdrops.<br><strong>\u25aa</strong> Swing, deflect, spin and power-hit your way through exciting <strong>baseball-style combat!</strong><br><strong>\u25aa</strong> Explore a vast world of unique and exciting environments, ultimately leading to a showdown with one of Bat Boy\u2019s brainwashed allies!<br><strong>\u25aa</strong> Take on the powers of each ally as you free them from the influence of Lord Vicious!<br><strong>\u25aa</strong> Glorious <strong>8-bit visuals</strong>, reminiscent of early platformer legends.<br><strong>\u25aa</strong> High-octane <strong>chiptunes from Evader Music</strong>, composer for <i>Smelter</i> and <i>Super Sami Roll</i>.<br><strong>\u25aa</strong> Dozens of enemies, exciting bosses and intriguing companions to encounter!<br><strong>\u25aa</strong> Baseball-bat-based traversal and environmental puzzle solving!<br><strong>\u25aa</strong> Hidden secrets, collectibles, unlockable music and more to find!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709350/extras/gemdrop2.gif?t=1713411028\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Strike One","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709350/4d3d37871f5553f8fdf740e9b9c61d46304ebb18.jpg"},{"name":"Strike Two","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709350/c6d0a85ea798ec10727f423bc69472fa8f8d6571.jpg"},{"name":"Strike Three","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709350/eb490fa6f9b4bee0c8f66fcb72ffe593758dacaa.jpg"},{"name":"Informed Buyer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709350/dc05166b8f3fa7401d5a27e2611894d7d4222f0b.jpg"},{"name":"A Taste For Music","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709350/d9635a12100a6821f76f093f94dbe97b3c3bf806.jpg"},{"name":"Melomaniac","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709350/1ddbad69adb7d9e32f40e5d5eea52eb24746e664.jpg"},{"name":"Seed from a Stran